ActCustoms Act
SubjectCPFTA Verification of Origin Regulations
PrecisCPFTA VERIFICATION OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS in order to incorporate the CANADA-PERU FREE TRADE AGREEMENT (CPFTA) into Canada's existing regulatory framework by allowing customs procedures related to rules of origin to be administered in accordance with the terms of the CPFTA.
